{"tid":103504,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[鐵膠出城回帶]3日廣島EVA新幹線快閃之旅","createTime":"2017-02-01T11:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T10:02:13.000Z","uid":49868,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b572aedc7fd26ea0345efb33fbe003290a39c1f5","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"上年剛剛好呢個時間返黎.....順手係連登試下出遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前係高登出過，不過d圖死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少廢話多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s9iuja0p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs9iuja0p&h=35c0e0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUO當時開左廣島線無耐，當時重落大雨，地勤派雨衣，不過我無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架機重要泊到老遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nazgxmj4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnazgxmj4&h=b0e4b2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三個幾鐘到廣島，咁岩見到KA既A320<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/io3492x1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fio3492x1&h=1cd426cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到廣島都係落雨，last day臨走先好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0ug4fpis\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0ug4fpis&h=fb85d88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ikteqnf0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fikteqnf0&h=5d84a633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次住既新廣電酒店，廣島電鐵開既，lobby重有廣島電鐵手信賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef02596ba1204b7c084cca49afd6deccb2cf9092","tid":103504,"uid":42881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fe9823563a2adbc18d6b9a32cd181f725c9cc3","tid":103504,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e35fb3076ae6a75e44aefd325a6b02abffa16b","tid":103504,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"留多次名先, 雖然睇過但鐵膠既野睇極都唔會厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9affc4f1aaa876f6e126b20eea7d343c10915237","tid":103504,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"間酒店房係我見過最細嘅日本酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67726f65b9314dfa63b309c2a717cdf0b12e6ae0","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1wxnjkmu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1wxnjkmu&h=f73bd4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣島山口pass，11000yen任坐5日博多至三原既新幹線(在來線下關至尾道)<br />\n我係坐回本兼有突好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z5ohtmya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz5ohtmya&h=3d704ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去博多既N700a，咁大個仔第一次坐新幹線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zb0pgdmx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzb0pgdmx&h=ad458926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內籠同台灣高鐵差唔多，話哂近親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i95r2u3j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi95r2u3j&h=1743edf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個幾鐘到博多，影一影對面九州既N700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c8cced362f4272fa426541bc973343818e9bd0","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間酒店房係我見過最細嘅日本酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係單人房，不過夠開個20吋喼既"},{"pid":"d32e7aad5be72acc88e4febc20d6a167af681969","tid":103504,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1257f26383c206c536afe895ce62633dcd5043cb","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5mwb294r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5mwb294r&h=06d0f7fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到博多8點幾，唔知食乜既情況下搭地鐵去天神見到mister donut，好滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zq0olks3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzq0olks3&h=a4d380ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去Rilakkuma Store行下，最鍾意鼻窿雞同角落生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/plkho508\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fplkho508&h=a1d0d256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完返博多站，對面既700系Railstar<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/garc4v1z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgarc4v1z&h=2a891c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6styxz8k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6styxz8k&h=3f5f96fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次坐Mizuho，九州既N700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gz60m3np\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgz60m3np&h=91364faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近距離J下Railstar個logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c29f47313674f40a2465050a1450d858b309b3","tid":103504,"uid":2630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n準備三月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a65a3fb6eeb941cbb9762d051e547f560f51699","tid":103504,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"冇住博多？"},{"pid":"4e1f0adf889ab799177ebd463baf676e34952e75","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇住博多？</blockquote><br />\n無，但三日有兩日都過左博多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c4a251e1bffbe58d09a713f5c56d8afa716f06","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/azx73n0i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fazx73n0i&h=0cdeb41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到廣島行過在來線個邊睇下，廣島色既115系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hgq1wx4y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhgq1wx4y&h=0f5d7eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇左陣出返廣島站前，新款既廣島電鐵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3fi7oqgy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3fi7oqgy&h=66fa9064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊款d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0mb7q9y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0mb7q9y&h=2511785a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w46rpgi9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw46rpgi9&h=112105af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d9vgfxh4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd9vgfxh4&h=0086f84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行返酒店途中既橋底有間食廣島風御好燒既鋪仔，膽粗粗入去試下，又幾好食<br />\n麵底好食過大阪風既粉底"},{"pid":"830f013ddfd1b33c2aa4a83a8174544cc2d5081e","tid":103504,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"你個POST我記得睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6967a1ff57c72aa1dea9772f3faef9bbdaede7","tid":103504,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"係唔係仲去左EVA CAFE到食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f567d85c80c7ca37d997cbbd1c43f8296dcdbef8","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係仲去左EVA CAFE到食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abf5bf1af46fd25d069ff607dbede1230595071","tid":103504,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係唔係仲去左EVA CAFE到食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSORLY<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac2b23275f461310061b63288b8c0a667014c42","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Day2</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jqde9nrs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjqde9nrs&h=330f6eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一早出發，另一隻色既115系<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nt410rlj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnt410rlj&h=d58cdca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早午餐都係佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ecy6frl5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fecy6frl5&h=c5acef41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目的地到著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ik014c36\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fik014c36&h=70a35f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮島口碼頭有兩間公司過宮島，松大汽船同JR，JR pass就包埋JR宮島航路；<br />\n廣島電鐵pass/Hiroshima Tourist pass就包松大汽船(後者包埋JR宮島航路)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i4e2v5ou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi4e2v5ou&h=f3f7dbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子殺人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v2pl506a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2pl506a&h=aa4aee7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zc12b6id\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzc12b6id&h=c275fb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行出去出面等，橫風橫雨好撚凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得5度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e66b58be58e1ade016e3fb5a1fe2b931ad36eed","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1zwld0k8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1zwld0k8&h=4f1161da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風大大雨濛濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f5z7oqxm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff5z7oqxm&h=95b66266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJR宮島航路同松大汽船最唔同係JR渡輪會特登駛近個大鳥居，再配埋解說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ja4mbepu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fja4mbepu&h=a1a8f4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落雨後見到彌山結哂冰，就諗起個排香港有班柒頭上去大帽山睇冰結果跣到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過累撚埋班消防員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kv3zrg0f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkv3zrg0f&h=870279a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能因為落雨，宮島無乜人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lg2xstou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flg2xstou&h=e8d14e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平清盛，將嚴島神社發揚光大既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/62vfcl91\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F62vfcl91&h=eccc1ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宮島最值得去既三個地方，可惜只去左一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" c