mbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgnixvuow&h=f48f098e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完就返博多站返廣島，月台影車少不了<br />\n仍然未有機會坐既九州新幹線800系<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ryc5u97h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fryc5u97h&h=8081b57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nbd7xat0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnbd7xat0&h=4d871d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次坐700系，Hikari<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3hvwlfce\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3hvwlfce&h=e2a389c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aqvrej3s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faqvrej3s&h=fe110b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到廣島，好肚餓，決定坐廣島電鐵入市內睇下重有無野食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/59p6g4r3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F59p6g4r3&h=3a4a0645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b41vuq08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb41vuq08&h=24a30aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果去左すき家食類似吉野家牛肉火鍋既定食，680yen算平喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r6azo72q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr6azo72q&h=2d2e2402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kxhlrbtz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkxhlrbtz&h=3469290a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完就坐尾班電車返廣島站，重有全日本最大既路面電車網絡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j9ht3ibu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj9ht3ibu&h=14b94cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xhq9fypn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxhq9fypn&h=e90d2f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到酒店見到雪糕自助售賣機就整返支，正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hzxjm9r5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhzxjm9r5&h=78397d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅神炸雞+麒麟啤=絕配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/30lky156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F30lky156&h=101cb2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後有C1格鬥送宵夜，做戲多過真打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d9a6c7aa945dea60e97cd6ec61544f793f8735","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酒店住邊到？</blockquote><br />\n「今次住既新廣電酒店，廣島電鐵開既，lobby重有廣島電鐵手信賣」<br />\n出左廣島站行5分鐘唔駛"},{"pid":"6edcd70f1eb686b7d57af5beed2991771625e7ec","tid":103504,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/30lky156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F30lky156&h=101cb2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後有<span style=\"color: red;\">G1</span>格鬥送宵夜，做戲多過真打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332aacffaa9f28c393b30ac6d358658b2d8b6cb9","tid":103504,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"dcaec61123e01cc2d23ef360c530fc66d